								class="w-full object-cover h-64"
							/>
						</figure>
						<div class="card-body">
							<h4 class="card-title text-white">
								For Musicians & Producers
							</h4>
							<p class="text-gray-300">
								Music videos, live performance coverage, promo
								content, and brand photography that captures
								your sound visually.
							</p>
						</div>
