							class="max-w-sm rounded-lg shadow-2xl"
						/>
						<div>
							<h3 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white mb-4">
								Visuals That Amplify Your Voice
							</h3>
							<p class="text-lg text-gray-300 mb-6">
								Imagine having professional visual content that
								tells your story authentically. That's what we
								create — photography, video, and audio that
								captures your essence and moves your audience.
